BEGIN_PGML_SOLUTION

[```\newcommand{\amp}{&}
\begin{aligned}
[$expression]\amp = \sqrt[[$n]]{[$x]\cdot [$y]}\\
\amp = \sqrt[[$n]]{[$x]}\cdot \sqrt[[$n]]{[$y]}\\
\amp = [$answer]
\end{aligned}
```]

